        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p>
                    
                    <bibl><ptr target="#gasperini1967a"/>, p. 167, n. <citedRange>10</citedRange>, fig. 194 
                    (=<bibl><ptr target="#gasperini2008"/>, p. 79, n. <citedRange>10</citedRange>, fig. 10</bibl>)</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>106950</citedRange></bibl>.
                    Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#stucchi1967"/>, pp. <citedRange>143-145</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#laronde1987"/>, p. <citedRange>169, footnote 13</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#purcaro2001"/>, p. <citedRange>31</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#maffre2007"/>, n. <citedRange>26</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
              </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><space atLeast="4" unit="character"/> <w lemma="δεκάτα">Δεκάταν</w> 
                    <persName type="divine" ref="#Apollo"><name nymRef="#Ἀπόλλων">τὠπό<supplied reason="lost">λλωνι</supplied></name></persName> 
                    <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"><certainty locus="name" match=".."/></gap>
                </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>Dîme consacrée à Apollon <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">par</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
                <p>Tithe dedicated to Apollo <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">by</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
                <p>Decima dedicata ad Apollo <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">da</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>For a parallel with the accusative <foreign xml:lang="grc">δεκάταν</foreign> and the dative of the god's name with the subaudible verb <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἀνέθηκε</foreign>
                    and no dedicant's name, see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr030200</ref> and probably also <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr006400</ref> and <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr107800</ref>.</p>
            </div></body>
